<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>Add Pictures</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="body">
            <div class="header"> 
                <div class="logo-pos">
                    <a href="/view"><b>My Photo Blog</b></a>
                </div>
                <div class="other-links">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/signup"><b>Sign Up</b></a></li>
                        <li><a href="/signin"><b>Sign In</b></a></li>
                        <li> <a href="/add"><b>Add Pictures</b></a></li>
                        <li> <a href="/logout"><b>Sign Out</b></a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="midder">
                <div class="write-up">
                    Building.... <br>
                    You're creating your pic-folio <br>
                    Your pictures speak about you! <br>
                </div>
                <div class="form-pos">
                    <form class="form" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                        <label for="pname">Picture name:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="pname" name="picname"><br>
                        <label for="desc">Description:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="desc" name="desc"><br>
                        <label for="pic">Add Picture: </label>
                        <input type="file" id="pic" name="pic" multiple><br>
                        <input type="submit" id="submit" value="Submit">
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <div class="quote">
                    <div>
                        <b>“It is only when they go wrong that machines remind you how powerful they are.”</b>
                    </div>
                    <div class="author">
                        <em>- Clive James, Broadcaster and Journalist</em>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="copyright">
                    Copyright @Emmrys
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                margin: 10px;
                height: 100vh;
            }

            label {
                display: inline-block;
                width: 100px;
            }

            .body {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: space-between;
            }

            .header {
                background-color: #ffee00c7;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                align-items: center;
                padding: 0 20px;
                height: 100px;
            }

            ul {
                display: flex;
                list-style: none;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 20px;
            }

            a {
                text-decoration: none;
                color: black;
            }

            .footer {
                background-color: #ffee00c7;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: space-evenly;
                align-items: center;
                height: 100px;
            }

            .midder {
                display: flex;
                height: 600px;
                justify-content: space-evenly;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .form-pos {
                border: 20px;
                border-radius: 3px;
                border-color: black;
                margin: 20px;
            }

            .quote {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                font-weight: 700px;
                justify-content: right;
            }

            .author {
                text-align: right;
                text-decoration: wavy;
            }
        </style>
    </body>
</html>